					methodology of online courses.This system enables an employee to
					overcome any technical gaps by learning new technologies. It aims
					to empower learners with skills which will help them get an edge in
					their careers and improve their lives. <br><br></br>
				</p>
				<br />

				<h3>How does it work?</h3>

				<p>Virtusa V-Learn application is intended to provide
					educational solutions for learners through a single gateway using
					the internet as the sole medium. It enables enablers to design a
					course with detailed study material in form of text documents,
					videos, audios, etc. A learner can browse through the available
					courses in course calendar and study interested courses. Post
					learnings a learner can take self-assessments on the respective
					course. After completion of each course the learner need to take
					final assessment. A learner can check the final assessment schedule
					and exam center information in the examination module.</p>
